{"title":"order by 多字段排序","date":"2018-08-11T01:52:00.000Z","link":"post/192","categories":["DataBase"],"updated":"2019-04-27T13:04:15.650Z","content":"<p>####问题</p>\n<p>先以<strong>class</strong>字段分组，然后再按照<strong>userscore</strong>排序，如果<strong>userscore</strong>中数值相同 就按照<strong>userid</strong>降序排序</p>\n<p>###表结构<br><img src=\"/usr/uploads/2018/08/3072343315.png\" data-action=\"zoom\" class=\"img-rounded img-responsive\"><br> <a id=\"more\"></a></p>\n<h3 id=\"答案\">答案<a href=\"post/192#答案\"></a></h3><p><img src=\"http://pqiuhq1tw.bkt.clouddn.com/322292185.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"原理\">原理<a href=\"post/192#原理\"></a></h3><p>ORDER BY 语句用于根据指定的列对结果集进行排序。</p>\n<p>ORDER BY 语句默认按照升序对记录进行排序。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"使用Mybatis时，在插入一条数据记录返回主键id值","link":"post/206"},"next":{"title":"Git Branch(分支)","link":"post/188"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/192/"}